& [ExecutionGatePreviewCliDesign] is the design contract for a non-mutating execution gate preview command
  @ [source_design] coordination/worker_execution_gate_design.sop
  @ [record_model] src/negotiated_agent/execution_gate.py
  @ [manager_job_notice] coordination/manager_job_notice.sop
  @ [created_at] 2026-05-29T19:45:00Z

  + [design_status] is ready_for_implementation_slice
  + [authority_boundary] is execution_gate_preview_design_not_gate_write
  + [primary_goal] is let operators or future worker loops inspect the deterministic gate decision before writing gate evidence or executing work
  + [non_goal] is Manager authorization writing
  + [non_goal] is Shaliach clearance writing
  + [non_goal] is worker implementation execution
  + [non_goal] is target workspace mutation

& [PreviewInputs] is what the command must accept
  + [required_arg] is project_root
  + [required_arg] is manager_authorization_ref
  + [required_arg] is shaliach_clearance_ref
  + [required_arg] is lease_ref
  + [required_arg] is current_frontier or active conversation lookup
  + [optional_arg] is gate_id
  + [authority_boundary] is input_refs_not_trusted_without_parse

& [PreviewParsingBoundary] is how evidence is read
  + [parse_target] is ManagerAuthorizationRecord fields from an existing SOP file
  + [parse_target] is ShaliachExecutionClearance fields from an existing SOP file
  + [parse_target] is WorkerLeaseRecord fields from an existing SOP file
  + [parse_target] is active current_frontier from ConversationSurface when current_frontier arg is omitted
  + [parse_rule] is reject missing required fields instead of guessing
  + [parse_rule] is preserve refs exactly as operator supplied them in output
  + [authority_boundary] is parser_not_semantic_validator

& [PreviewOutput] is the only allowed command output
  + [stdout_artifact] is ExecutionGateDecision.to_sop()
  + [exit_code_zero] is preview command parsed inputs and produced a decision, even if gate_status is blocked
  + [exit_code_nonzero] is input parse failure or missing file
  + [write_behavior] is no files written
  + [authority_boundary] is preview_output_not_execution_permission
  = must: leave manager authorization, Shaliach clearance, lease, claims, read cursors, active conversation, and worker cycle files unchanged
  = must: include execution_gate_decision_not_completion_approval in stdout

& [ImplementationOrder] is the safe next split
  + [slice_1] is add SOP field loaders for ManagerAuthorizationRecord, ShaliachExecutionClearance, and WorkerLeaseRecord
  + [slice_2] is add execution gate preview CLI and tests proving no files are written
  + [slice_3] is add PowerShell wrapper after CLI behavior is stable
  + [slice_4] is only later consider explicit gate decision writer
